    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem I\u2019m parting with! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, it still has that 'new car' feel. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014not a single blemish or scratch to be found. It\u2019s truly the cleanest ride you\u2019ll find out there, and it runs like a dream. I'm looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 47500.0,
