    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example is mechanically superlative: the VANOS system has been fully rebuilt with Beisan components, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates. The factory-original Laguna Seca Blue paint retains a deep luster, and the underside is remarkably clean, showing no signs of corrosion or fluid seepage. Performance is sharp thanks to a fresh set of bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the precise steering geometry these cars are known for. All VIN tags are present, and the rod bearing service is documented. This is a turn-key, concours-level driver for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Pristine condition. Single owner. Full service history. Garage kept. No accidents. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
