    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade masterpiece in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, glass-like factory finish without a single swirl mark or stone chip. The interior remains in a 'time-capsule' state, featuring pristine leather that still carries that new-car scent, untouched bolsters, and flawless dashboard accents. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified specialists, with a complete portfolio of records to prove its pedigree. From the matching-numbers drivetrain to the untouched spare tire and original toolkit, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity to own a virtually brand-new example of a modern classic. Includes two keys, all original manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained in impeccable showroom condition and reflecting the highest standards of automotive care. This unit boasts a flawless exterior and a pristine interior, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. Meticulously inspected and certified by our master technicians, it represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection. Available now for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
