    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next big adventure. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the full dealership price tag, this is the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
