      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is a superlative E46 M3, showcasing a level of mechanical preservation rarely seen. The S54 3.2L inline-six delivers blistering performance with its individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained double-VANOS system, ensuring a linear power band up to the 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally sound with proactive subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that remains tight and responsive. This vehicle is in concours condition, featuring a flawless undercarriage and an engine bay free of heat-cycle fatigue. A definitive collector-grade example for the purist driver.",
